It has been a genuinely enriching experience interning at BISAG-N over the past two months. The guidance from our external guide, Dr. Abdul Jhummarwala, was invaluable — his support helped us navigate every stage of our project, "Virtual Reality Based Clothing TryOns," from initial research to a working prototype.
