Beyond the technical learning, this internship gave us a real understanding of how a national institute like BISAG-N contributes to India's geo-spatial and emerging-technology landscape, under the leadership of Shri T.P. Singh and the broader BISAG-N team. It was a well-rounded, hands-on experience that balanced independence with strong mentorship.
We are truly grateful for this opportunity and would highly recommend this internship to future students of Gati Shakti Vishwavidyalaya.
